'''國際設計大獎'''（{{Lang-en|'''International Design Awards'''}}）是一個為了挖掘更多設計人才由[[Lucie_foundation|Lucie foundation]]在美國[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亞州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉磯]]創立的獎項<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.traveldailynews.asia/news/article/58602/millennium-amp-copthorne-hotels-tokyo|title=Millennium & Copthorne Hotels' Tokyo property reports strong performance; clinches design award|accessdate=1 June 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150720121636/http://www.traveldailynews.asia/news/article/58602/millennium-amp-copthorne-hotels-tokyo|archivedate=2015年7月20日|df=}}</ref>。獎項分類包括職業組以及學生組的建築、室內、產品、圖像、時尚設計等，獎項本身與許多美國著名的雜誌及媒體合作得以讓得獎者有各種宣傳設計作品的平台，是設計新血以及職業設計人試著登上舞台的橋梁之一<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pressreleases.triplepointpr.com/2014/07/17/livescribe-3-smartpen-takes-gold-in-eighth-annual-international-design-awards/|title=Livescribe 3 Smartpen Takes Gold in Eighth Annual International Design Awards|accessdate=1 June 2015|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307113049/http://pressreleases.triplepointpr.com/2014/07/17/livescribe-3-smartpen-takes-gold-in-eighth-annual-international-design-awards/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.howdesign.com/design-competition-galleries/international-design-awards/|title=International Design Awards|publisher=HOW Design|accessdate=2016-11-01|archive-date=2018-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181118092643/http://www.howdesign.com/design-competition-galleries/international-design-awards/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailysabah.com/science/2015/04/13/turkish-team-shines-in-international-design-awards-in-la|title=Turkish team shines in International Design Awards in LA|accessdate=1 June 2015|publisher=Dailysabah.com|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234810/http://www.dailysabah.com/science/2015/04/13/turkish-team-shines-in-international-design-awards-in-la|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

